	   <tr><td colspan=2>You must be going about it wrong. I am level 29 and have a 135 skill in tinkering. I am already making Aqua Lungs that trivial at 148. Rebreathers may trivial at 177+<br><br>The trick with any skill is to only make the next higher level item. That is to say if you are making Mechanical Lockpicks and trivial at 62, then start making Flameless Lanterns until you trivial at 68. Do not attempt Bow Cams that trivial at 75 until you trivial those Flameless Lanterns. Yes you will succeed at the higher items, but not enough to make it worth the added cost.<br><br>Mabbena Taseldwyn<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
