	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm sure the initial posters of this thread have already answered their own questions, but here's a response for anyone else.  Yes, Gnomes start with Tinkering 50.  No, you can't begin to work on it until 16th (tho you can still make lo-triv items).  And finally, no, there is no level cap - you could make rebreathers at level 16.<br><br>I'm at Tinkering 95.  With a CHA of 105+, this cost roughly 3kpp.  That's 3000pp.  This is not a tradeskill for the weak of finger or light of pocketbook.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
